			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="color: red"><span style="font-size: 24px; line-height: normal">Air Pet</span></span>
<br />

<br />
<a href=http://www.magecompendium.com/library/pets-air-library.html>Download this for Offline Viewing</a>
<br />

<br />
<HR>
<br />

<br />
<img src="http://www.magecompendium.com/library/images/airpet.jpg" border="0">
<br />

<br />
Below 50, Air is a defensive pet, sporting high AGI but low HP. Below level 50 it casts the stun <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=967&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Air Elemental Attack</a>. Above level 50 its stun <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=1020&amp;source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Air Elemental Strike</a> gains a DD component. Air also features a near-immunity to cold based attacks.
<br />

<br />
<HR>
<br />

<br />
<CENTER><span style="color: red"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: normal"><a name=petstats></a>Pet Statistics</span></span></CENTER>
<br />
<span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal">Special thanks to all mages that helped compile this list.</span>
